**Cultist Wolf** | Werewolf Group | Transformation
__Basics__
The Cultist Wolf is a wolfpack member who is a part of the cult.
__Details__
If any of the members of the cult group would become werewolf-aligned, their role changes to Cultist Wolf.
The Cultist Wolf is a member of the cult: they can vote on the cult's kill polls. The Cultist Wolf does not retain any other abilities its previous role had.
The Cultist Wolf is strongly disguised as their previous role.

__Simplified__
The Cultist Wolf is a wolfpack member who is a part of the cult.

__Formalized__
TBD

__Card__
The Cultist Wolf leads a double life and gets the benefit of listening along with the enemy.
